Package edu.cmu.cs.crystal.tac Description

The interfaces for the three-address code (TAC) instructions. If you are writing a flow analysis, you may find TAC easier to use that the Eclipse AST. TAC has no sub-expressions and uses temporary variables to break up complex expressions in the AST into simpler expressions. To create a flow analysis using TAC, implement either ITACTransferFunction or ITACBranchSensitiveTransferFunction.
